{"tid":1967943,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"[離教心路歷程] 返左十幾年學校教會，發覺舊約聖經根本係邪教","createTime":"2020-04-11T09:46:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-06T11:56:01.000Z","uid":353419,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"55d722b7478e5a8914598ecdd37924cf1177b847","tid":1967943,"uid":353419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T09:46:42.000Z","msg":"<strong>舊約聖經好鼓吹殺人，任何罪行都會處以血腥殘暴的死刑，哪怕你唔聽父母話，都要用被石頭扔死，非常極端。</strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/phSa4f3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FphSa4f3.png&h=09204946&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<strong>原來為左令下凡天使唔好比平民輪姦，推自己兩個女出去做代替品，係耶和華眼中竟然係義人。</strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dvmSyao.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdvmSyao.png&h=b86d40cc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<strong><br />\n阿伯拉罕的故事，根本就係活人獻祭，就算最後冇殺到，但最後拎隻羊獻祭，全善的神有冇考慮隻綿羊的感受？</strong><br />\n<br />\n <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ipBbOKO.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FipBbOKO.png&h=a777a70b&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<strong>耶穌都發覺唔對路，所以聲稱係神的兒子，廢除哂舊約。舊約話以牙還牙，耶穌話被打左臉要比埋右臉，新約理念完全抵觸舊約，偏向於佛教的普道眾生。</strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/89t5Tin.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F89t5Tin.jpg&h=b6f2f70c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong>好彩基督教有新約中和返，如果唔係會變到以色蘭教咁，佢地只信舊約聖經，搞到打聖戰又出好多恐怖份子。<br />\n</strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3CPppyd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3CPppyd.jpg&h=beff7e7a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong>舊約聖經反映左古代猶太人的封建野蠻，耶和華只係猶太人創造的角色。奴隸制，反同性戀，啲思想跟唔上文明進步。相較之下，佛教捨己為人，不殺生，尊重選擇自由的，其思想更善良，值得信服。</strong>"},{"pid":"73061fbb14d619f925a69af62c655c9f5547eaf8","tid":1967943,"uid":88817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T09:49:01.000Z","msg":"心路歷程呢？"},{"pid":"4b2cf5094e28009e4470f3719c2aa653dae24652","tid":1967943,"uid":185606,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T09:54:22.000Z","msg":"屌你成本舊約聖經都抄人嘅，抄完人又嫌人哋暴力又剩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92a2955553d44b309b8d34f2bd83441b00c97633","tid":1967943,"uid":353419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"73061fbb14d619f925a69af62c655c9f5547eaf8","tid":1967943,"uid":88817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T09:49:01.000Z","msg":"心路歷程呢？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T09:56:35.000Z","msg":"出面的教會比較品流複雜，我都係返中學的團契，自己老師同學一齊圍爐好撚正，現代基督徒主要係跟新約。"},{"pid":"deaca63eba9bb0fad8ff3790276e453d24ddbb22","tid":1967943,"uid":117722,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T09:59:54.000Z","msg":"BBC講過有古經文指耶穌童年去過西藏學佛<br />\n教庭一知道即刻毀屍滅跡<br />\n咁啱聖經入耶穌童年係消失左"},{"pid":"a32eff23809e08d22b8e40abf272ffc028c8e0be","tid":1967943,"uid":353419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"deaca63eba9bb0fad8ff3790276e453d24ddbb22","tid":1967943,"uid":117722,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T09:59:54.000Z","msg":"BBC講過有古經文指耶穌童年去過西藏學佛<br />\n教庭一知道即刻毀屍滅跡<br />\n咁啱聖經入耶穌童年係消失左"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T10:02:38.000Z","msg":"有可能，新約入面的耶穌咁溫柔，係因為融入左佛教思想，其實釘十字架咪姐係我不入地獄誰入地獄。"},{"pid":"fc4ce61e97ed2822429e79c4128127d50aa74447","tid":1967943,"uid":191926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T10:16:36.000Z","msg":"只信舊約=猶太教<br />\n極端排外<br />\n<br />\n無新約聖經<br />\n今日無咩人信<br />\n<br />\n歐洲會繼承多神體系"},{"pid":"c2b63a882a803119267d59ead87f955b02441d62","tid":1967943,"uid":191926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T10:17:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>只信舊約=猶太教<br />\n極端排外<br />\n<br />\n無新約聖經<br />\n今日耶教應該無咩人信<br />\n<br />\n歐洲可能仍然保持<br />\n多神體系</blockquote>"},{"pid":"2522e519b59c18af38f86f14263f0b0a2e6ace66","tid":1967943,"uid":53666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"scor